Swipe ➡️ At 90, Barby Keel has rescued over 10,000 animals in her 54 years running the Barby Keel Animal Sanctuary in Sussex, UK. 🐾🥺

Starting in the 1970s with one dog, she now cares for over 600 animals. Despite battling cancer three times, she never takes a day off.

Her 12-acre sanctuary is volunteer-run and Barby says she has no plans to slow down anytime soon.

(📸 via SWNS)
